  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Identification of 131 corona infected people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Health has informed that the number of corona infected people in the country is increasing day by day.",
        "Hemanta Herath, Deputy Director General of Health Services, Ministry of Health, said this.",
        "He also said that 131 corona infected people have been identified yesterday.",
        "The Deputy Director General of Health Services has also announced that the rate of corona infections is increasing compared to the daily number of corona infections. (a)"
      ],
